[49m[38;5;10m+    198[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    199[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    200[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    201[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: enrollment and consent (with cross-institution-sharing granularity), longitudinal-store initialization, multi-source integration with continuous data ingestion, channel entry with disclosure, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading with cross-institution data assembly, conversation handling with operationally-grounded responses, output safety screening with scope verification, escalation routing across multiple pathway types, and audit logging with cross-institution access tracking.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    202[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    203[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    204[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── ENROLLMENT + CONSENT ──────────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    205[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    206[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient enrolls via institution portal, care team      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    207[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    referral, or care management program]                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    208[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Documented consent specific to care coordination,    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    209[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      reviewed by legal counsel                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Granular consent for cross-institution data sharing  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      (in-network only, in-network plus selected partners, │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      broad TEFCA-style sharing, etc.)                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent for care-team information flow               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Privacy posture explained in plain language          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - State-specific consent variations enforced           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: signed consent record; enrollment confirmed;   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    longitudinal store initialized]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-coordinator longitudinal store]                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions (across all consented sources)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications (across all prescribers)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active provider relationships                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active referrals with state                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Open orders (labs, imaging, procedures)              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pending prior authorizations with status             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scheduled appointments across all providers          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounters across all settings                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient preferences                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent posture (per source, per data class)         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-coordination intensity per care plan            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── MULTI-SOURCE INTEGRATION ──────────────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous data ingestion]                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Institution EHR: scheduled FHIR pulls plus event-    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      driven webhooks                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Partner-system EHRs: SMART-on-FHIR app integration   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      where consented                                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - HIE feeds: subscription-based event delivery         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Claims data: payer feeds (where ACO or payer-driven  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      deployment)                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy fill data: 277-CA or vendor integration     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - ADT messages: HL7 v2 ADT subscription                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prior-authorization queues: payer integration        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - External lab and imaging results: HL7 ORM/ORU or     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      FHIR DiagnosticReport                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Referral lifecycle events: from referral-management  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      system                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Per-source consent enforcement]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Every retrieval call validates patient consent for   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      the source and data class                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Audit record of consent-validated retrieval          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Cross-source reconciliation jobs]                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Medication reconciliation                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Problem-list reconciliation                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Allergy reconciliation                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Appointment reconciliation                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Discrepancies surfaced to care team                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: reconciled longitudinal record refreshed       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    on schedule and on event]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
