[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, per care plan]                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-discharge day three check-in                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-referral day seven status check                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Day-before-appointment preparation reminder          │
