[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY + EMERGENCY SCREENING ────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection (with source-fencing for  │
