[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous emergency screening]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute symptom disclosures (chest pain, shortness of  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      breath, severe pain, neurologic deficits) route to   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      triage workflow (recipe 11.6)                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Suicidal ideation routes to mental-health crisis     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      pathway (recipe 11.8)                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute medication reactions route to clinical team    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    327[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Sensitive-disclosure detection]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    328[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Intimate-partner violence indicators                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    329[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Elder-abuse indicators (mandatory-reporting trigger  │
