[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    347[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Cross-source context retrieval]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    348[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active conditions (from all consented sources)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    349[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Current medications (from all consented sources)     │
